Title: PSSLS: Parallel Solution of Sparse Least Squares Problems
Body: MIME-Version: 1.0 Server: CERN/3.0 Date: Sunday, 24-Nov-96 23:03:10 GMT Content-Type: text/html Content-Length: 881 Last-Modified: Thursday, 17-Oct-96 19:55:18 GMT PSSLS: Parallel Solution of Sparse Least Squares Problems PSSLS(Parallel Solution of Sparse Least Squares Problems) is a sparse matrix package for solving large, sparse, linear least squares problems on distributed-memory machines.
